OL,3,C'Fellowship' formed to share tales of
OL,4,Cmissing Stone of Destiny fragments
OL,6,FA group of 18 people whose families
OL,7,Fwere given missing fragments of the
OL,8,FStone of Destiny have come together to
OL,9,Fshare their stories, forming the
OL,10,F"Fellowship of the Stone".
OL,12,FThe fellowship gathered from across
OL,13,FScotland and England as a research
OL,14,Fproject sought to trace the hidden and
OL,15,Foften surprising journeys of each of
OL,16,Fthe fragments.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
