OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776999825
OL,3,C'Fellowship' formed to share tales of
OL,4,Cmissing Stone of Destiny fragments
OL,6,FLast year, she appealed for anyone
OL,7,Fwith links to the fragments to get in
OL,8,Ftouch, and in March she decided to
OL,9,Fbring together several people who had
OL,10,Fdone so, as well as other researchers
OL,11,Fand historians.
OL,13,FThe event organised through the
OL,14,FUniversity of Stirling led to the
OL,15,F"Fellowship of the Stone" being
OL,16,Fformed, as the 18 people gathered to
OL,17,Fdescribe how each of their families
OL,18,Fcame to have part of the ancient
OL,19,Fsandstone block ` which have often
OL,20,Fbeen passed down in secret through
OL,21,Fgenerations.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
