OL,3,C'Fellowship' formed to share tales of
OL,4,Cmissing Stone of Destiny fragments
OL,6,FWriting about the event, Prof Foster
OL,7,Fsaid: "Perhaps the highlight of the
OL,8,Fday was when we all stood around the
OL,9,Flarge display table and everyone told
OL,10,Ftheir stories, picking up and sharing
OL,11,Fwhat they had brought along.
OL,13,F"Indeed, the earlier excitement, as
OL,14,Feveryone unpacked their bag, in one
OL,15,Fcase a suitcase, and we waited eagerly
OL,16,Fto see what would appear.
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
