PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776999825
OL,3,C'Fellowship' formed to share tales of
OL,4,Cmissing Stone of Destiny fragments
OL,6,F"With prior knowledge of most of their
OL,7,Fstories, I arranged it so we could see
OL,8,Fhow new understandings of the life of
OL,9,Fthe stone were emerging, and how they
OL,10,Ffitted in."
OL,12,FAn expert from National Museums
OL,13,FScotland examined the fragments which
OL,14,Fwere brought to the fellowship event
OL,15,Fin early March, saying there is no
OL,16,Fgeological reason to doubt their
OL,17,Fauthenticity.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
