OL,3,C'Fellowship' formed to share tales of
OL,4,Cmissing Stone of Destiny fragments
OL,6,FWhen the King was coronated in 2023,
OL,7,Fthe Stone of Destiny was taken to
OL,8,FLondon and mounted in the Coronation
OL,9,FChair, continuing its ancient role in
OL,10,Fthe monarchy.
OL,12,FIt moved to Perth Museum in 2024,
OL,13,Fhaving previously been kept at
OL,14,FEdinburgh Castle.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
